1. *Osveta* je slatka kad je zaslužena. (Revenge is sweet when deserved.)
2. Nije mi stalo do *osvete*. (I don't care about revenge.)
3. *Osvetu* ne treba uzimati u svoje ruke. (Revenge shouldn't be taken into your own hands.)
4. Ona traži *osvetu* za ono što joj je učinjeno. (She seeks revenge for what has been done to her.)
5. *Osvetnički* plan je bio veoma precizan. (The revenge plan was very precise.)
6. U filmu, glavni lik je bio opsednut *osvetom*. (In the movie, the main character was obsessed with revenge.)
7. *Osvetoljubivost* nije osobina koju bih cijenio kod ljudi. (Vindictiveness is not a trait I value in people.)
8. Njegova *osveta* je bila okrutna i nepravedna. (His revenge was cruel and unjust.)
9. Nakon što su ga izdali, osjećao je samo *osvetu* u svom srcu. (After they betrayed him, he only felt revenge in his heart.)
10. Iako je znao da nije u pravu, nije mogao da sakrije svoju *osvetoljubivost*. (Even though he knew he was wrong, he couldn't hide his vindictiveness.)

(Note: The word "osveta" in Serbian means "revenge" or "vengeance", while "osvetnički" means "vindictive" and "osvetoljubivost" means "vindictiveness".)